{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"To have an understanding of the range of different organisations which fulfil the different safety functions"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"To have an understanding of a typical sale and the purchase process"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"To have a general understanding of English Law in areas where the broker will be involved"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"To understand the importance of health and safety for the yacht broker"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Understand the importance of good relations"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"To have an overview on the different types of brokerage companies and their advantages and disadvantages"}}
