{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Certifying Authority Limited)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For a yacht or small craft requiring a code compliance certificate, the Owner applies directly to the organisation of his"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"choice for his craft to be surveyed. For this service the organisation selected will charge a fee and a nominated surveyor"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"will attend the yacht to carry out the survey. Depending upon the organisation chosen the actual approach to the survey"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"may differ but in all cases the subject matter for the survey will be the same as detailed in the code. Subject to the craft"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"complying with the code, a certificate of compliance is subsequently issued."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For all craft where either regulation or codes apply, failure to adhere to the requirements can lead to prosecution which"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the MCA carries out through its enforcement division (not through the certifying authority)."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For a yacht broker working in the commercial craft area of the industry it is vital that they possess an understanding of the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"requirements of the regulations and the methods by which yachts are certified."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In the event of an accident involving loss of life or environmental pollution, at some stage the MCA may become involved."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"There is, however, one other government organisation that is involved specifically in the investigation of accidents. This is"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the Marine Accident Investigation Branch (MAIB)."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Yacht Brokerage"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Module 1"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"16"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Marine Accident Investigation Branch"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The MAIB is the government organisation that investigates marine accidents within the United Kingdom and abroad for"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"accidents involving United Kingdom registered vessels and for marine accidents in UK waters. It is the role of the MAIB to"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"investigate and report, not to prosecute. Inspectors are drawn from the nautical, marine engineering, naval architecture"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and fishing disciplines and are appointed under the Merchant Shipping Act 1995. An administrative staff deals with"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"records, data analysis and publications and provides general support to inspectors at all stages of an investigation."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The powers of MAIB inspectors and the framework for reporting and investigating accidents are set out in the Merchant"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Shipping Act 1995. The Merchant Shipping (Accident Reporting and Investigation) Regulations 1999 put the framework"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"into effect."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"These regulations are the foundation of the MAIB\u2019s work. They apply to merchant ships, fishing vessels and (with"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"some exceptions) yachts and small craft. They define accidents, set out the purpose of investigations and lay down"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the requirements for reporting accidents. The regulations make provision for the ordering, notification and conduct of"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"investigations, but allow inspectors a good deal of discretion. In carrying out their investigation, the MAIB has extremely"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"wide powers and failing to assist can be a criminal offence. Following the investigation, the MAIB reports its findings to the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Secretary of State and subsequently will publish a report on the accident. If there are breaches of regulations identified in"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"this report the MCA or other relevant government departments (such as the Health and Safety Executive) may then take"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"over and prosecute."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The MAIB publishes the results of every investigation. The MAIB also produces a Safety Digest, a collection of short reports"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"on the lessons learned from investigations in order to reduce the potential of future such accidents recurring."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In the ordinary course of events the broker will not normally become involved with the MAIB. However, in the event of"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"an accident involving serious injury or loss of life on board a yacht, exactly where an MAIB investigation will lead is rarely"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"a certainty."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Recreational Craft Directive"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For members of the European Economic Area (EEA) on 16 June 1998 the Recreational Craft Directive (RCD) entered into"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"force. Subsequently the Directive was updated by Directive 2003\/44\/EC. The directive, which is part of European Law,"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"applies to almost all recreational craft between 2.5m and 24m. As a result of the directive it is the responsibility of anyone"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"placing such a craft on sale within the European market to ensure that it meets the requirements of the directive. As with"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"all such directives there are some exclusions such as craft intended solely for racing, canoes, kayaks, gondolas, pedalos,"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"sailing surfboards, historical replicas, experimental craft, craft built for the Owner\u2019s own use if not sold within 5 years,"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"submersibles, hovercraft and hydrofoils. The primary aim of the directive was to remove barriers to trade within Europe"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and not, as some might suggest, to impose a minimum safety standard on recreational craft."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In order to comply with the directive, craft must meet 29 essential safety requirements (ESRs). However, for simple craft"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"many of these requirements are not applicable. Craft can meet a particular ESR by complying with the relevant harmonised"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"standard. However, there are also other routes to achieve compliance."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Within the directive there are four design categories:"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"A"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Ocean."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"B"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Offshore."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"C"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Inshore."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"D"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Sheltered Waters."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Builders of categories A, B and C have to use \u201cnotified bodies\u201d (similar in some respects to certifying authorities) to assess"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"conformity. Builders of category D are allowed to carry out self assessment."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Providing that the craft meets all relevant ESRs it can then carry the CE mark."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In the UK enforcement of the directive is carried out by the Trading Standards Office and failure to comply may result in"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"a fine."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For a broker, understanding the Recreational Craft Directive and how it applies is one of the basics of day to day business."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"17"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"A builder\u2019s plate showing the CE mark"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Classification Society"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Another organisation that is mentioned frequently and is often misunderstood is the Classification Society of which Lloyd\u2019s"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Register, Det Norske Veritas and the American Bureau of Shipping are probably the best known. Frequently, Classification"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Societies are regarded as a standard that has to be achieved (and maintained) and all too often people misunderstand"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"that the standard only applies to certain aspects of a vessel."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Classification Societies all work to sets of published Rules that define the minimum acceptable standards for certain"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"aspects of different types of craft considered relevant by the particular society. Most of the major Classification Societies"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"have specific rules for yachts and small craft but in fact it is not true that all, or indeed any, craft must comply with these"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"rules."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"When a yacht is built to Class this means that the design and construction of the yacht has followed the specific rule"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"requirements of the Classification Society. It does not mean, however, that every aspect of the yacht has been considered"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and evaluated by the Classification Society. The only way to determine what is or is not included is to refer to the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Classification Society\u2019s Rules as applicable to the particular craft."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Of particular importance to note is that the Classification Society\u2019s Rules do not detail the minimum level of fire fighting"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"equipment or lifesaving equipment that a yacht or small craft needs to carry."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The ten most prominent Classification Societies belong to a grouping called the International Association of Classification"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Societies (IACS). The 10 member organisations are: -"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"American Bureau of Shipping (ABS)*"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Bureau Veritas (BV)*"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"China Classification Society (CCS)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Det Norske Veritas and Germanischer Lloyd (DNV GL)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Korean Register of Shipping (KR)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Lloyd\u2019s Register of Shipping (LR)*"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Nippon Kaiji Kyokai; ClassNK (NKK)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Registro Italiano Navale (RINA)*"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"\u2022"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Russian Maritime Register of Shipping (RS)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"* indicates whether that society has specific types of yacht or small craft"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"One final area of misunderstanding is the role that Classification Societies play in Flag State regulation. Some Flag States"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"delegate some or all of their statutory inspection functions to Classification Societies. In such cases, a classification surveyor"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"can survey the craft and issue a certificate on behalf of the Flag State (provided the craft complies with the Flag State"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"regulations). When working in this role the class surveyor is, in effect, the same as a Flag State surveyor. However, the same"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"surveyor can (and often does) at the same time carry out the classification survey and issue the classification certificates."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Therefore, at one time the surveyor can be fulfilling two different roles. One is a statutory role where certification is"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"compulsory, the other is a classification role where certification is not mandatory."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"It is this second area where confusion sometimes arises when a vessel is issued with a safety equipment certificate by a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"class surveyor. In this case the certificate only means that the craft complies with the relevant Flag State regulations. It"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"does not mean that the classification society has approved the safety equipment. As already stated, classification society"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"rules do not normally cover the minimum requirements for fire fighting and lifesaving equipment that needs to be carried."}}
