{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Yacht Racing Organisations"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Many pleasure yachts take part in racing whether this is at local club level or at an international level. Provided such craft"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"are pleasure craft, as has already been emphasised, there is no minimum safety requirement. Therefore, yacht racing"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"organisations set and monitor a minimum level of safety compliance."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Almost all yacht clubs have their own specific \u2018safety rules\u2019. The extent of these are directly proportional to how litigious the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"particular country is, with the US and the UK being numbers one and two. The International Sailing Federation lists a very"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"large number of affiliated sailing\/racing clubs. Most of the clubs mentioned include their own, club specific, safety rules."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"WORLD SAILING"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For sailing yachts the International Sailing Federation (ISAF) (originally known as the International Yacht Racing"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Union) the governing body for the sport of sailing established in Paris in 1907 sets the minimum safety"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"standards see http:\/\/www.sailing.org"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Other organisations, both not-for-profit and commercial, organise specific races and\/or events. These include the Royal"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Ocean Racing Club, Royal Yachting Association, Clipper Round the World and the SAEM Vend\u00e9e for the Vend\u00e9e Globe."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Each one imposes specific safety requirements for the competitors that roughly equate to the risk envisaged during"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the race."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Other Organisations and Schemes \u2013 RNLI, RYA, BSS"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In the United Kingdom two other organisations have a particular interest in yacht safety. These are the Royal National"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Lifeboat Institution, the Royal Yachting Association. In addition, the Environment Agency and British Waterways introduced"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the Boat Safety Scheme. They all approach safety from completely different directions."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"1"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Royal National Lifeboat Institution is the organisation that voluntarily goes to the aid of seafarers in"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"distress at sea. Therefore, the organisation is uniquely placed to identify from first-hand experience where"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"yacht safety breaks down. The organisation is maintained by voluntary donation and, therefore, needs to"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"be particularly cautious with how it uses the money it is given. As rescuing people has a high risk to both life and property,"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the RNLI recognises that a proactive approach to yacht safety can help to reduce the risk to life and hence the number of"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"times their services are called for. As a result, the \u201cSea Check Safety Scheme\u201d was introduced whereby experienced and"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"trained individuals are made available to yacht Owners to discuss and advise upon the minimum levels of safety"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"equipment that a craft should carry."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Royal Yachting Association on the other hand is an organisation that represents yacht and small craft"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Owners. In essence, it believes that education is better than regulation and among other things it provides"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"a framework for the education and training of yacht and small craft Owners. As part of its educational"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"process the RYA publishes the \u201cBoat Safety Book\u201d booklet that recommends a minimum level of safety equipment that a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"yacht and small craft should carry."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The Boat Safety Scheme was established in 1997 by the Environment Agency and British Waterways to"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"promote safety on the inland waterways. The scheme sought to set minimum standards in respect of boats"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and their on board installations and components. At the same time it became compulsory to obtain a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"navigation licence and to demonstrate having third party liability insurance. Boats using the inland waterways"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"are required to have a Boat Safety Scheme Examination and on successful completion are issued with a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"certificate that is valid for four years."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"It is important to emphasise here that none of the above organisations or authorities operates in a vacuum. There is"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"frequent and close co-operation between organisations with the common purpose of ensuring the safety of life of those"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"who go afloat in yachts. Nevertheless, as already emphasised, no clearly defined single minimum standard exists that is"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"compulsory for yachts used solely for leisure purposes."}}
