{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"3. THE PURCHASE OF A YACHT"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The primary function of the yacht broker is to bring a willing buyer (purchaser) of a yacht together with a willing seller"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"(vendor) and thereby earn a commission on achieving a successful sale. The following section is a general guide to a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"typical sale and purchase process. It is not meant to imply that this is the only way a yacht is bought or sold and, indeed,"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"there are many individual variations of the general process described."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Finding the Right Type of Yacht"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The range of craft available to a prospective buyer is enormous, as is the experience level of the prospective Owner."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Generally speaking, a yacht is a luxury item and frequently both sale and purchase can be very emotive. Some of the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"factors that should be considered before a purchase include intended use, budget and level of previous experience. After"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"this come more specific questions such as need for a crew, where the craft is to be kept and how much time and money"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the maintenance of the boat will require."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"As a broker taking an instruction for a sale it is important to establish the Owner\u2019s requirements. Whilst this is a statement"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"of the obvious, it is not uncommon to start the sale process only to find that when it comes to actually parting with the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"yacht, the Owner does not really want to sell! Take time to discuss your prospective client\u2019s requirements and draw from"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"your own experience and preferences to offer advice and assistance where appropriate."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For a first time seller with absolutely no experience (other than having bought the yacht in the first place) there are several"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"books and guides published on buying a yacht and these are also an excellent source of advice for selling."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Broker\u2019s Listing"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Methods of selling a yacht divide into two categories, the private sale through classified advertisements and\/or the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"internet or sale through a yacht broker."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Classified advertisements can be found in most of the monthly yachting journals and locally in the windows of chandlers"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and boat yards (where the boat yard or chandler does not operate a brokerage)."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For the Owner wishing to sell the craft, the advantage of a private sale is the fact that there will be no brokerage"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"commission when the sale is concluded. However, the disadvantages are that more time is involved in promoting the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"craft, organising viewing and discussing details, that there is not such a wide reach for potential customers for the sale and"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the fact that there is no one who can offer expert advice to help with the sale."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For the buyer it might mean a slightly cheaper purchase but also more problems in concluding the deal and a greater"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"level of uncertainty of the right of the seller to proper legal title for the craft."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For either type of sale, caution is required in how the yacht is described. The Trade Descriptions Act requires an accurate"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"representation of the yacht in any advertising. Therefore, excellent condition means just that and if there is dirt in the bilge"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"the yacht is not in excellent condition!"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For the Owner selling through a broker the advantages and disadvantages are reversed in that there is better exposure"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"to potential customers and greater help with the sale but potentially less money because of payment of the brokerage"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"commission (although this latter point maybe largely offset by the skill of the particular broker in achieving the right price)."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For the buyer the brokerage sale means that he may pay more than for a private sale and also, more importantly, the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Owner (vendor) now has a broker representing him whereas the buyer is on his own (unless he uses a surveyor)"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Montage of different magazines that advertise yachts for sale"}}
