{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"displacement of the vessel. Rather it is an approximate measurement of the internal volume against a defined set of rules."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In both the commercial and yachting spheres a number of different formulae have been used over the years. Under the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"current Tonnage Regulations yachts of under 24 metres use a simplified version of the \u2018international formula\u2019 to determine"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"tonnage, with no distinction being made between \u2018gross\u2019 and \u2018net\u2019 or \u2018registered\u2019 tonnage. A tonnage certificate can then be"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"issued by a certifying authority and it is only compulsory for tonnage to be measured if the vessel is to be Part I registered."}}
