{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Contract"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Most people are familiar with the idea of a contract whether it is to buy a boat, a car or a packet of sweets. In all cases a number"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"of distinct factors are present and these factors decide whether or not any particular contract is valid. A contract does not need"}}
