{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"For a broker, the contract with the client (vendor) is what sets out the rules by which the broker will work and be paid."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Most brokers use a standard set of terms and conditions that are widely accepted throughout the industry and make every"}}
