{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The role of common sense for the yacht broker"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Health and safety is everybody\u2019s concern but it can all too frequently be ignored or simply dismissed. Each individual has"}}
