{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"order to note its details. Whilst the broker is engaged actively to pursue a particular goal (that of looking at the yacht and"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"preparing an inventory), it is important that appropriate consideration is given to his own personal protection, to the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"protection of others and to preservation of the environment. Much of this comes under the general title of the application"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"of common sense. Situations differ but on every occasion when a broker sets out to undertake a job he should take time"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"to consider a range of different factors."}}
