{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Appropriate preparation before inspecting a yacht is essential."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The weather may not initially seem to be terribly relevant until the first time you carry out an inspection on a cloudless day"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"in summer without adequate skin protection or during a freezing day in winter without adequate protection against the"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"cold. Once you become absorbed in a looking at the yacht, it is sometimes possible to lose track of time. Both sunburn"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"and hypothermia are progressive and only become apparent once it is too late and the damage has been done. Weather"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"forecasts are easily available so it always pays to check the forecast and make certain that you are properly prepared to"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"cope with the anticipated weather. Included in this section is the wind. Is it really sensible to carry out an inspection on a"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"yacht that is standing ashore when the wind is blowing gale force 8 across a bleak and open shoreline? How much value"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"will you gain from trying to carry out an inspection of the outside of the craft during a rain or snow storm?"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Location of the yacht plays a major part in the safety of the broker. Many yachts are located in modern marinas with"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"excellent facilities and good, safe access. However, initial inspections may be carried out in quite different locations. A"}}
