{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"but it is meant to show the possible alternatives that may need to be considered."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"A yacht on dodgy supports"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Carrying out an inspection of a yacht on a tidal mud flat might be the only realistic method of finding out the information"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"that is required for a listing. However, in such a circumstance the broker needs to be particularly aware of the specific risks of"}}
