{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"Access and Use of Ladders"}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"When a boat is ashore all but the smallest will normally require some means of portable access to gain entry to the inside"}}
