{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"In the UK a sole trader is responsible to account for his earnings to both the Inland Revenue and Contributions Agency."}}
{"prompt":"An Introduction to Yacht Brokerage","examples":{"text":"The greatest single advantage to being a sole trader is the lack of requirements in respect of legal documentation and"}}
